\id 1TI - Zanaki 1 Timothy 
\h 1 Timoteo 
\toc3 1 Timoteo 
\toc2 1 Timoteo 
\toc1 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya Pauro ku Timoteo 
\mt2 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya Pauro ku 
\mt1 Timoteo 
\imt1 Obhutaangiro 
\ip Enyaarubha yino yakaamirwe na Pauro. Akamukaamira omuutu wuno yaari akubhirikirwa Timoteo, wuno akatuuribhwa kwe enzira ye emirimo gya Pauro, nikyo kikoriri Pauro aramubhirikira Timoteo kubha, omwaana waaye we eheene mubhwiikirirya. Timoteo ahaageendania na Pauro mumirimo myaaru gyo okurwaaza Amangʼana Amazomu iguru wa Yeesu Krisito (\xt rora Amahokya ga Abheega 17:14-15, 18:5\xt*). Pauro hano yaari akyaari kukaama enyaarubha yino, akamuha Timoteo emirimo gyo okwiimeererera abhiikirirya mumugye gwa Efeso. 
\ip Obhugirirye bhwa Pauro okukaama enyaarubha yino, bhwaari ni kumubhuurira Timoteo kyeego ekweenderwa okusora no okweegya abhakaruka bhe ekanisa na abhasakirya. Pauro akeenda kubha, abhakaruka bhabhe abhaheene, bheegye obhuheene ne eteemo nzomu kubhiikirirya. Kweeki aramusabha ewe hamwe na abhiikirirya bhoosi bhabhe, bharasabhira abhaatu bhoosi, kumasabhi ga maanga goosi. Ekitabhu kino kireegya abhiimeerereri bha amakanisa bhabhe na amanaga okwaanga ameegyo goosi go orurimi. Kweeki kina amaragiriryo maaru gano gakunagya kusakirya abhiimeerereri bha makanisa eziisiku zino okukaangata amakanisa gaabhu. 
\c 1  
\s1 Obhukeerya 
\p  
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Pauro, omweega wa Krisito Yeesu. Nitumirwe kubha omweega wa Krisito Yeesu kwo obhuswaagyo bhwa Taatabhugya Omutuurya weetu, na Krisito Yeesu niwe eriisigo ryeetu.  
\v 2 Nirakukaamira awe Timoteo, omwaana waane we eheene mubhwiikirirya. 
\p Orubhaango, ebhigoongi no omureembe okurwa ku Taatabhugya Taata, na ku Krisito Yeesu Omukuru weetu, bhibhe naawe. 
\s1 Obhurekya iguru wa ameegyo go orurimi 
\p  
\v 3 Hano natanwiiri kugya mumugye gwa Makedonia, nikakusabha wiikare mumugye gwa Efeso, nikakukumiirirya okubha obharekye abhaatu bhano bhakweegya ameegyo go orurimi.  
\v 4 Obharekye bhatige okugwaatirira amagano gano gatana bhweera, no okwiinyaakya no obhuzaabhi bhwa amariina ga bhazaazi gano gatana obhuteero. Amangʼana gayo goosi garakora obhuhakani, gatakusakirya abhaatu okumwiikirirya Taatabhugya, kyeego gari amiiseego gaaye go obhutuurya bhuno bhukutuukana no obhwiikirirya.  
\v 5 Obhugirirye bhwe eriiragiriro riyo ni kubha, abhiikirirya bhaseegane kwo obhuseegi bhwe eheene, kumitima mizomu no obhwiikirirya bhwe eheene.  
\v 6 Nawe abheegya abhaandi bhatigiri gayo, bhiikyooriri, bharagaamba amangʼana gano gatana bhweera.  
\v 7 Bhareenda bhabhe abheegya bhe emigiro\f + \fr 1:7 \fk Abheegya bhe emigiro\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* gya Musa, yiingabha gano bhakubhuga no okukumiirirya, bhatagamenyiri. 
\p  
\v 8 Nawe etwe tumenyiri kubha, emigiro gya Musa ni mizomu, kyeego omuutu araagituniirire kyeego ekweenderwa.  
\v 9 Kweeki, tureenderwa kumenya kubha, emigiro gitatuurirwe kubhe eheene, nawe kubhano bhakusarya emigiro na bhano bhakwaanga, kubhano bhatakumuseengera Taatabhugya na abhasarya. Na gyatuurirwe kubhano bhatakumwiigwa Taatabhugya na abhabhi, kubhano bhakwiita bhawiise na bhanina waabhu, na kubhiiti bha abhaatu,  
\v 10 kubhaseebheeti na bhano bhakuhiindira na abhasubhe abharikyaabhu kya abhakari, kubhano bhakuratira abhaatu no okubhagurya mubhutumwa, abhabheehi, na kubhano bhakwiirahira kwo orurimi. Emigiro gituurirwe kumangʼana goosi gano gatakweendana na ameegyo go obhuhoru.  
\v 11 Ameegyo gayo, garabhoneka mu Mangʼana Amazomu, gano gakweerekya obhuguungo bhwa Taatabhugya murubhaango rwoosi. Amangʼana gayo nigo nikahaabhwa na Taatabhugya nibharwaazire. 
\s1 Omureembe gwa Yeesu Krisito ku Pauro 
\p  
\v 12 Nirabhuga, “Ozomirye, Krisito Yeesu Omukuru weetu.” Ewe akaaniha amanaga, kwo okubha akaanimenya ni muheene no okunisora nibhe omuhokya waaye.  
\v 13 Na yiingabha kubhutaangiro hayo, nikamutuka no okunyaakya abhaatu bhaaye, niari omuzabhuri, nawe ewe akaanirorera ebhigoongi. Akakora ego, kwe ekigirirye niari nirakora gayo kwo obhugeege na nitaari no obhwiikirirya.  
\v 14 Eheene Omukuru weetu Krisito Yeesu akaanitweera ebhite bhukongʼu, kweeki akaaniha obhwiikirirya no obhuseegi kwo okugwaatana neewe. 
\p  
\v 15 Engʼana yino ni ye eheene, na ereenderwa okwiikiriribhwa kubha, “Krisito Yeesu akaaza mukyaaro, okubha atuurye bhe ebhibhi.” Na gati we ebhibhi bhayo, enye neenye nikoriri ebhibhi kukira bhoosi.  
\v 16 Nawe kwe ekigirirye kiyo, Yeesu Krisito akaanirorera ebhigoongi! Akaanierekya okwiikongʼeererya kwaaye kweenye we ebhibhi kukira bhoosi, okubha nibhe ekireengyo kubharya bharaamwiikirirye no okusuungʼaana obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.  
\v 17 Ambe, Taatabhugya niwe omutemi wuno atana obhuteero, atakukwa, naabhe atakurorekana, na niwe omweene. Ewe asuungʼaane obhusuuku no obhuguungo kirakeego na kirakeego. Gabhe ego. 
\s1 Pauro aramuswaagya Timoteo okugwaatirira amaragiriro 
\p  
\v 18 Timoteo omwaana waane, nirakuha amaragiriro gano, kuriingʼaana na amangʼana go obhurooti gano gaagaambirwe iguru waazo. Amangʼana gayo gakusakirye kye ekigwaato mwiihi rya Taatabhugya izomu.  
\v 19 Ogwaatirire obhwiikirirya no omutima muzomu. Abhaatu abhaandi bharegiri okukora garya bhamenyiri kubha ni heene, riyo rikoriri bhatige obhwiikirirya bhwaabhu.  
\v 20 Mubhaatu bhayo arimu Himenayo,\f + \fr 1:20a \xt Rora 2 Timoteo 2:17-18.\f* na Arekizanda. Bhayo nibhatigiiri Seetaani\f + \fr 1:20b \ft Obhugazuro bhwa \fk nibhatigiiri Seetaani \ft ni kubha Pauro akabhaanga okugeenderera kugwaatana hamwe na abhiikirirya mukanisa.\f* okubha bheege, bhatige kumutuka Taatabhugya. 
\c 2  
\s1 Ameegyo iguru yo obhusabhi mumakanisa 
\p  
\v 1 Ambe, obhweemero bhwa goosi, nirakusabha awe hamwe na abhiikirirya bhoosi mubhe murasabhira abhaatu bhoosi, kumasabhi ga maanga goosi. Kweeki, mubhe muramubhuurira Taatabhugya “Ozomirye” kwiiguru ya abhaatu bhoosi.  
\v 2 Mureenderwa kubhasabhira abhatemi na abhaandi bhoosi bho obhukaangati, okubha twiikare kwo omureembe, tumutuniirire Taatabhugya no okubha ne eteemwa nzomu.  
\v 3 Eriingʼana rino ni zomu, kweeki riramuzomera Taatabhugya Omutuurya weetu.  
\v 4 Ewe areenda abhaatu bhoosi bhatuuribhwe, no okumenya obhuheene.  
\v 5 Tumenyiri kubha gayo ni go obhuheene, kwo okubha ariho Taatabhugya wumwe ego, no omuutu wumwe wuno okwiigwaania abhaatu na Taatabhugya, neewe ni Krisito Yeesu.  
\v 6 Ewe akaruusya obhwiikari bhwaaye omweene, okubha abhatuurye abhaatu bhoosi. Bhuno nibhwo obhweerekenio bhuno Taatabhugya akatuha, kwiibhaga rino yateeriho.  
\v 7 Na kwe ekigirirye kiyo, enye nikatuurwa kubha omweega nigeende okurwaaza no okweegya bharya bhatari Abhayahudi amangʼana go obhwiikirirya no obhuheene. Niragaamba ge eheene, nitakugaamba orurimi. 
\p  
\v 8 Kweego, ahagiro hoosi hano mukwiikumania kusabha, ndeenda abhasubhe bhagororokye amabhoko iguru okusabha. Bhakore ego kwa amiiseego mazomu, bhasabhe bhatana obhuhaari naabhe kuhakana.  
\v 9 Kweego ndeenda abhakari bhiibhoohe kyeego ekweenderwa, bhabhe ne eteemo nzomu na kusuuhu. Bhataseega kungʼarira kwo okusuka eziinzweeri,\f + \fr 2:9 \fk Okusuka eziinzweeri, \ft ku Kizanaki bhaari bharabhuga, okuruka kaswa.\f* kasi kwo okwiibhoha ebhigiro bhye ezahaabu na bhino bhikubharyabharya, kasi eziingibho zyo obhuguri bhukuru.  
\v 10 Nawe bhabhe ne eteemo nzomu, kyeego bhakweenderwa abhakari bhano bhiikiriirye kumuseengera Taatabhugya.  
\v 11 Hano abhakari bhakubha bhareega, bhabhe abhiitegeereri na abhiigwa.  
\v 12 Nitakubhaha abhakari omweeya gwo okweegya naabhe okukaangata abhasubhe, nawe bhabhe abhiitegeereri.  
\v 13 Niragaambeego, kwo okubha Taatabhugya akabhuumba Adaamu kubhweemero, okumara Haawa.  
\v 14 Naabhe Adaamu ataangʼeenereerwe, nawe omukari niwe akangʼeenererwa, akasarya obhuswaagyo bhwa Taatabhugya.\f + \fr 2:14 \xt Rora Obhweemero 3:1-6.\f* 
\v 15 Nawe abhakari bharasuungʼaana obhutuurya kwe enzira yo okwiibhura abhaana, kyeego bhakugeenderera kwiikara mubhwiikirirya, obhuseegi, obhuhoreeru no okubha na kusuuhu. 
\c 3  
\s1 Omukumo gwa abhiimeerereri bhe ekanisa 
\p  
\v 1 Eriingʼana rino ni rye eheene, “Omuutu wuno areenda emirimo gyo okubha omwiimeerereri we ekanisa, wuyo yiigoombiri emirimo emizomu.”  
\v 2 Ambe, omwiimeerereri we ekanisa, abhe omuutu wuno atakusororibhwa. Abhe no omukari wumwe ego, abhe na kusuuhu, kweeki abhe wa amangʼeeni, omuutu wuno akusuukwa, musaambaaruku, no omuutu wuno amenyiri okweegya.  
\v 3 Atabha omunywi omuraara, atabha omurwaani, abhe munyoohu wuno aseegiri omureembe. Kweeki atabha wuno aseegiri eziimbirya.  
\v 4 Abhe omwiimeerereri omuzomu we enyuumba yaaye, bhano bhamenyiri okweegya abhaana eteemwa yo okwiigwa no obhusuuku.  
\v 5 Eraabhe omuutu aratamwa okwiimeererera enyuumba yaaye omweene, aranagyabhwi okuriibha abhiikirirya mukanisa ya Taatabhugya?  
\v 6 Kweeki, atabha omwiikirirya omuhya, ataaza okwiizuungya. Okwiizuungya kuyo kuramukora atinirwe ekiina kyeego Seetaani\f + \fr 3:6 \fk Seetaani\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* akatinirwa ekiina.  
\v 7 Nawe, abhe omuutu wuno akugaambwa bhuzomu naabhe na abhaatu bhano bhatari Abhakrisito, okubha ataaza kubha na amasoro no okutiimbwa mukitiimbo kya Seetaani. 
\s1 Omukumo gwa abhasakirya bhe ekanisa 
\p  
\v 8 Abhasakirya bhe ekanisa nabho, bhabhe ne eteemwa nzomu, bhatabha abhabheehi, bhatabha abhanywi abharaara, bhatabha bhano bhaseegiri eziimbirya.  
\v 9 Nawe, bhabhe abhaatu bhano bhakugwaatirira obhuheene bhwo obhwiikirirya bhweetu kwo omutima muzomu.  
\v 10 Bhayo nabho, bhasakibhwe obhutaangiro. Na bharirorekana kubha bhatana amasoro, niho bhakore emirimo giyo.  
\v 11 Kweego, abhakari bhaabhu\f + \fr 3:11 \fk Abhakari bhaabhu\ft , obhugazuro obhuundi bhuratura kubha, \fqa abhakari abhasakirya.\f* bhabhe bhe eteemo nzomu, bhatabha abhamoonyi, bhabhe na kusuuhu, bhabhe abhaheene mumangʼana goosi.  
\v 12 Abhasakirya bhabhe no omukari wumwe wumwe, na bhabhe bhariimeererera bhuzomu abhaana bhaabhu na abhaandi bhano bhari munyuumba yaabhu.  
\v 13 Bharya bhano bhakukora emirimo gyo obhusakirya bhuzomu, bharabha bharasuukwa. Hayo bharaabhe no obhukaari bhwaaru bhwo kuraarika amangʼana go obhwiikirirya bhwaabhu mu Krisito Yeesu. 
\s1 Obhuheene bhwo obhwiikirirya bhweetu 
\p  
\v 14 Nirakukaamira amangʼana gayo, yiingabha niriisiga okuuza owaazo bhwaangu hano.  
\v 15 Nawe nirikeezera, omenye gano bhakweenderwa abhaatu okukora munyuumba ya Taatabhugya. Abhaatu bhayo nibho ekanisa ya Taatabhugya wuno ari muhoru, ne ekanisa niyo etimu no obhurusa bhwo obhuheene.  
\v 16 Obhuheene bhuno Taatabhugya yeerekirye ni bhwo okuruguurya, neebhwo ni bhuno, 
\q1 Krisito akiiyeerekya kwo omubhiri gwaaye, 
\q1 akeerekibhwa ne Ekoro kubha omuheene, 
\q1 akarorekana kubhamaraika,\f + \fr 3:16 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Rora engʼana \ft \+it maraika\+it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* 
\q1 akarwaaza mubhyaaro bhyoosi, 
\q1 akiikiriribhwa na abhaatu mukyaaro kyoosi, 
\q1 akagegwa okugya iguru mubhuguungo. 
\c 4  
\s1 Abheegya bho orurimi 
\p  
\v 1 Bhoono, Ekoro Muhoreeru aragaamba atakubhisa kubha, muziisiku zyo obhuteero, abhaandi bharaaza okutiga obhwiikirirya bhwe eheene, no okutuniirira eziikoro zyo obhungʼeenererya, na ameegyo ga amasaambwa.  
\v 2 Ameegyo gayo, gareegibhwa na bho orurimi, kweeki bho orurimi bhano emitima gyaabhu gikuuri kyeego gyookiibhwe kwe ekyooma kyo omuriro.  
\v 3 Bhayo bharabharekya abhaandi kubha bhatige okukweera, kasi kurya ebhyaakurya ebhiindi. Nawe Taatabhugya akabhibhuumba okubha bhisuungʼaanwe kwo okuzyomya na abhiikirirya, kwo okubha bhamenyiri obhuheene.  
\v 4 Ebhigiro bhyoosi bhya Taatabhugya ni bhizomu, naabhe kitariho kyo okwaangwa. Bhyoosi bhisuungʼaanwe kwo okuzyomya,  
\v 5 kwo okubha eriingʼana rya Taatabhugya na amasabhi geetu, garabhikora ebhigiro bhiyo bhyeeribhwe. 
\s1 Omubhagati omuzomu wa Yeesu Krisito 
\p  
\v 6 Oraabhahe abhahiiri bheetu ameegyo gano, hayo niho oraabhe omuhokya omuzomu wa Krisito Yeesu. Kweeki orabha okiiniiri bhuzomu mubhuheene bhwo obhwiikirirya bhweetu na mumeegyo amazomu gano ogatuniiriiri.  
\v 7 Otigane na amagano ga abhaatu bhe ekare gano gatari ge enyaangi gano gatana bhweera, nawe wiinarye okwiikara kyeego Taatabhugya akweenda.  
\v 8 Emenyekeeni kubha, “Okunarya omubhiri okubhona amanaga, kuno obhweera hasuuhu. Nawe, wiinarye okwiikara kyeego Taatabhugya akweenda, bhuriho obhweera bhwa maanga goosi, kwo okubha bhuratuha obhurage bhwo okubhona obhuhoru bhwa bhoono na bhuno bhukuuza.”  
\v 9 Engʼana yiyo ni ye eheene, abhaatu bhareenderwa bhasuungʼaane.  
\v 10 Riyo niryo riragirya turakora omukya, kwo okubha turamwiisigira Taatabhugya wuno ari muhoru, Omutuurya wa abhaatu bhoosi, kiindi bhano bhakwiikirirya. 
\p  
\v 11 Amangʼana gayo, ogeegye no okugaswaagya.  
\v 12 Omuutu wowoosi atakuzeera awe kwo okubha okyaari mumura, nawe okore omukya obhe ekireengyo kya abhiikirirya mubhugaambi, muteemo, na mubhuseegi, mubhwiikirirya na kwe eheene.  
\v 13 Okore omukya kusomera abhaatu Amakaamo Amahoreeru, orwaaze no okweegya, tee hano niraaze eyo.  
\v 14 Otatiga kuhokeerya obhuturo bhuno Taatabhugya akuheeri kuhitira amangʼana go obhurooti, eriibhaga okatuurirwa amabhoko na abhakaruka bhe ekanisa.  
\v 15 Ogwaatirire amangʼana gayo, okubha abhaatu bhoosi bharore omukya gwaazo mubhwiikari bhwaazo.  
\v 16 Wiiriibhe eteemo yaazo na ameegyo gaazo, no ogeenderere okukora ego. Hano okukora gayo oriituurya awe omweene na bhano bhakukwiitegeerera. 
\c 5  
\s1 Obhuswaagyo kubhiikirirya 
\p  
\v 1 Otabhiiyogya abhakaruka, nawe obhatoongere kyeego okutoongera wuuso weenyu. Abhamura obhatoongere kyeego abhahiiri bhaazo,  
\v 2 abhakiikuru kyeego nyoko weenyu, na abhaakya obhakorere kwe ekoro nzomu kyeego abhasubhaati bheenyu. 
\p  
\v 3 Obhasuuke abhatuumba bhano bhatana wo okubhasakirya.  
\v 4 Nawe, eraabhe omutuumba wowoosi ana abhaana kasi abhazukuru, bhayo bheege okusakirya abhahiiri bhaabhu. Hano bhakukora ego, niho bharariha abhiibhuri bhaabhu amazomu gano bhabhakoreeri. Ego niigo Taatabhugya akweenda.  
\v 5 Omutuumba wuno atana muutu wo okumusakirya, wuyo aramwiisiga Taatabhugya, aramuseengera no okumusabha Taatabhugya amusakirye obhutiku no omwiisi.  
\v 6 Nawe omutuumba wuno akuseega enaamba ye ekyaaro, wuyo akuuri yiingabha ararorekana muhoru.  
\v 7 Amangʼana gayo, obhabhuurire abhiikirirya, okubha bhataaza kubha na amasoro.  
\v 8 Nawe omuutu wowoosi wuno atakusakirya abhaatu bhaaye, kiindi bha munyuumba yaaye, wuyo arabha atigiri obhwiikirirya, kweeki abheeri mubhiihu kukira omuutu wuno atari mwiikirirya. 
\p  
\v 9 Omutuumba ariikiriribhwa okubharwa mubhatuumba, eraabhe ahikirye emyaaka kweemera miroongo esaasabha (60), kweeki yaari mukari wo omusubhe wumwe.  
\v 10 Abhe ano omukumo muzomu kumahokya gaaye. Abhe areriri abhaana bhaaye bhuzomu, abhe araginihya abhagini, abhe arabhiisaabhya abhahoreeru amaguru gaabhu, abhe arabhasakirya bhano bhakunyaakibhwa, kweeki abhe ariiruusya na yiibhanwiiri okukora amahokya amazomu. 
\p  
\v 11 Nawe, abhakari abhatuumba, otabhaha omweeya kusikira mubhubharwa, kwo okubha enaamba yo omubhiri erabhatama kukira okwiiruusya ku Krisito, hayo bhareenda okukweerwa.  
\v 12 Kwo okukora ego, bharabha bhatiniirwe ekiina, kwo okubha bhatigiri obhurage bhwaabhu ku Krisito bhwo okusaaga bhakyaari kukweerwa.  
\v 13 Abhatuumba kya bhayo, bhanariri eteemo yo obhutobhu, bharageendageenda muziinyuumba zya abhaatu. Kweeki, bharabha abhagwaatania no okwiisikirya mumangʼana ga abhaandi, eno bharabhuga amangʼana gano gatakweenderwa.  
\v 14 Bhoono, enye ndeenda abhatuumba abhasubhaati, bhabhe bharakweerwa, bhiibhure abhaana no okutuga eziinyuumba zyaabhu, okubha abhabhisa bheetu bhatige okutugaamba bhubhi.  
\v 15 Rora kubha abhatuumba abhasubhaati abhaandi bhamariri okubhura no okumutuniirira Seetaani. 
\p  
\v 16 Kyo omukari omwiikirirya ana abhatuumba mubhahiiri bhaaye, abhasakirye. Akore ego, okubha ekanisa etigwe kutamirwa, niho ekanisa erabha no omweeya gwo okusakirya abhatuumba abhaandi bhano bhatana obhusakirya. 
\p  
\v 17 Abhakaruka bhe ekanisa bhano bhakwiimeererera ekanisa bhuzomu, bhasuukwe no okukorerwa amazomu,\f + \fr 5:17 \fk Bhasuukwe no okukorerwa amazomu \ft ku Kiyunaani ni \fqa bhasuukwe maanga abhiri.\f* kiindi bhano bhakwiiruusya okurwaaza no okweegya engʼana ya Taatabhugya.  
\v 18 Niragaamba ego, kwo okubha ekaamirwe mu Makaamo Amahoreeru, “Engʼoombe hano ekuhuura engano, otayibhoha omunwa.”\f + \fr 5:18a \xt Rora Obhuhiiti bhwe Emigiro 25:4.\f* Kweeki ekaamirwe, “Omuhokya wuyo woosi areenderwa ahaabhwe amariho gaaye.”\f + \fr 5:18b \xt Rora Ruuka 10:7.\f*\fig Eziingʼoombe zirahuura engano|alt="oxen threshing grain" src="hk00096c.tif" size="col" loc="1Tim 5:18" copy="Horace Knowles © The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="5:18" \fig* 
\p  
\v 19 Otiikirirya amasemo iguru yo omukaruka we ekanisa, otana obhumenyeekererya bhwa abhaatu bhabhiri kasi bhatatu.\f + \fr 5:19 \xt Rora Obhuhiiti bhwe Emigiro 17:6, 19:15.\f* 
\v 20 Nawe abhakaruka bhe ekanisa bhano bhakugeenderera okukora amabhi, obharekye embere wa bhoosi, okubha abhaandi bhayo bhoobhohe. 
\s1 Obhurekya ku Timoteo 
\p  
\v 21 Nirakuswaagya embere wa Taatabhugya, ne embere ya Krisito Yeesu na bhamaraika abhasorwa kubha, ogwaatirire gayo, otatina ekiina kwa bhwaangu kasi okuseega orubhaara rumwe.  
\v 22 Otiikirirya kwa bhwaangu kumutuurira omuutu amabhoko akore emirimo gyo Omukuru, kwo okubha orimutuurira omuutu omubhi amabhoko, awe orabha wiisaangirye mubhubhi bhwaaye. Awe wiiriihe, okubha osaage kubha omuheene. 
\p  
\v 23 Kweemera bhoono, awe otanywa amaanzi ageene, nawe obhe oranywa na amaanzi go omuzabibu\f + \fr 5:23 \fk Amaanzi go omuzabibu\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* masuuhu kwiiguru yo obhurweeri bhwaazo bhwe enda na amarweeri agaandi gano gakukunyaakya. 
\p  
\v 24 Abhaatu abhaandi, ebhibhi bhyaabhu bhirarorekana kubhweero, naabhe bhakyaari kutinirwa ekiina. Nawe abhaatu abhaandi, ebhibhi bhyaabhu bhiibhisiri, bhirarorekana ibhaga riindi.  
\v 25 Egoego, amahokya amazomu gararorekana kubhweero. Na garya giibhisiri, garabha kubhweero. 
\c 6  
\s1 Obhuswaagyo kubhabhagati abhiikirirya 
\p  
\v 1 Abhagya bhoosi abhiikirirya, bhasuuke abhakuru bhaabhu, okubha eriina rya Taatabhugya na ameegyo geetu gatazeerwa.  
\v 2 Abhagya bhano abhakuru bhaabhu ni bhiikirirya, bhatabhazeera kwo okubha ebho ni bhahiiri. Bhareenderwa kubhahokeerya bhuzomu no okukira, kiindi kwo okubha bharabha bharabhasakirya abhiikirirya abharikyaabhu, kweeki ni bhaseegwa bhaabhu. Gayo obheegye no okurekya. 
\s1 Ameegyo go orurimi no obhuniibhi bhwe eheene 
\p  
\v 3 Bhariho abhaatu bhano bhakweegya ameegyo go orurimi. Bhareegya gano gatakwiikirirania na ameegyo go obhuheene bhwo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito, kweeki gatakwiikirirania na ameegyo gano gakubhakaangata abhaatu okumutuniirira Taatabhugya.  
\v 4 Bhayo bhiizwiiri obhwiizuungya, kweeki bhatamenyiri riyo ryoosi. Abhaatu bhayo bhariibhaamba haka zino zitana obhweera iguru ye ehingʼana hisuuhu. Mugayo gurarweeramu omugono, eriiyoge, amatuki, amiiseego mabhiihu,  
\v 5 kweeki eziisiku zyoosi garasarya obhwiigwaani. Abhaatu bhayo bhasarikiri obhwoongo, bhatana obhuheene. Bhariiseega kubha okumutuniirira Taatabhugya niyo enzira yo okubhona obhuniibhi. 
\p  
\v 6 Eheene, okumutuniirira Taatabhugya no okwiiswa ne ebhigiro bhino anabhyo, kuramukora omuutu abhone obhweera bhukongʼu,  
\v 7 kwo okubha mukyaaro muno, tutiiziri na kyokyoosi, naabhe tutakugya na kyokyoosi.  
\v 8 Ambe, eraabhe tune ebhyaakurya na bhyo okwiibhoha, twiiswe nabhyo.  
\v 9 Nawe bhano bhakweenda obhuniibhi, bharagweera mubhitiika, no okutiimbwa mubhitiimbo, na munaamba nzaru ye ekigeege. Eziinaamba ziyo zirabhasarya tee bhasike,  
\v 10 kwo okubha okuseega bhukongʼu eziimbirya nikwo obhweemero bhwo obhubhi bhwaaru. Abhaandi bhaseegiri obhuniibhi, bhangʼeenereerwe, bhatigiri obhwiikirirya, bhoono bhariireetera obhururu bhwaaru no okunyaaka mukoro. 
\s1 Obhurekya ku Timoteo 
\p  
\v 11 Nawe awe, omuutu wa Taatabhugya, ogaryaare gayo. Otuniirire obhuheene, obhusuuku bhwa Taatabhugya, obhwiikirirya, obhuseegi, obhwiikongʼeererya no obhunyoohu.  
\v 12 Orwaane eriihi izomu ryo obhwiikirirya, ogwaate obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Obhuhoru bhuyo, nibhwe okabhirikirirwa hano okiikirirya obhwiikirirya bhwaazo embere wa abhamenyeekererya bhaaru.  
\v 13 Nirakukumiirirya embere wa Taatabhugya wuno akubhiha obhuhoru ebhigiro bhyoosi, ne embere ya Krisito Yeesu wuno yaruusirye obhumenyeekererya bhwe eheene embere wa Pontio Pirato,  
\v 14 ogwaatirire obhuswaagyo bhuyo kwo okugiigwa no okutama okutitiikana, tee hano Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito araaze.  
\v 15 Okuuza kwaaye kuraabhe eriibhaga hano Taatabhugya yeendiri. Taatabhugya niwe araguungibhwa, ewe omweene niwe Omukaangati, niwe Omutemi wa abhatemi bhoosi, no Omukuru wa abhakuru bhoosi.  
\v 16 Ewe omweene niwe atakukwa, yiikeeri mubhweero bhuno omuutu atakunagya kubhwiisukiirira. Kweeki atariho omuutu wuno amuruuzi, naabhe wuno akunagya kumurora. Obhusuuku no obhunagya bhubhe bhwaaye, kirakeego. Gabhe ego. 
\p  
\v 17 Obhabhuurire abhaniibhi bhatige okwiiguungya, naabhe okwiisiga obhuniibhi bhwaabhu bhwe ekyaaro kino, bhuno ni bhwi ibhaga iguhi. Nawe bhamwiisige Taatabhugya wuno akutuha ebhigiro bhyoosi kwo obhusaambaaruku bhwaaye, okubha tubhihokeerye kwo obhuzomererwa.  
\v 18 Kweeki obhabhuurire bhakore amazomu, niho bhabhe abhaniibhi mumahokya amazomu. Bhabhe bhararuusya ebhigiro no okwiisaangya hamwe na abhaandi kubhigiro bhyaabhu.  
\v 19 Kwo okukora ego, bhariituurira ekibhuumbiko kyo obhurusa obhugumiru kuziisiku zino zikuuza, okubha bhasuungʼaane obhuhoru bhwe eheene. 
\p  
\v 20 Weyaa Timoteo, gwaatirira bhuzomu obhuheene bhuno oheerwe. Otige kwiisikirya mumangʼana gano gatari ge enyaangi na gatana obhugazuro bhwobhwoosi. Kweeki otiisikirya mubhuhakani bhwe ekigeege, gano abhaatu abhaandi bhariisiga kubha amangʼeeni.  
\v 21 Abhaatu abhaandi bhano bhagwaatiriri gayo, bhatigiri obhwiikirirya bhwaabhu. 
\p Orubhaango gubhe hamwe neemwe.